			(text_box private "Input power from receiver coil\n\n\nOutput pin, delivers power to the battery\nBootstrap capacitor for the rectifier. Connect capacitor 10nF/10V to AC1/2\nOpen-drain output. Active when BAT is enabled\nOvervoltage protection. Connect 0.47uF/25V capacitor to AC1/2\nOutputs for communication. Connect 22nF/25V capacitor to AC1/2\nSet priority between wireless and wired power (EN2 low = enables wired charging)\nInput for rectified power measurement\nBattery charge current\nPower ground\nFilter capacitors for the rectifier. Connect capacitor to PGND\nTermination current threshold\nTemperature sense and control\nExposed thermal pad"
				(at 60.96 10.16 0)
				(size 86.36 -45.72)
				(margins 1.016 1.016 1.016 1.016)
